The President of the African Development bank (AfDB), Dr. Akinwumi Adesina, has celebrated his wife, Grace Yemisi Adesina, on her 60th birthday anniversary.  Adesina in a tweet, celebrated his wife as the best friend in the world and a treasure in his life. Adesina in a message on his official twitter handle wrote: Akinwumi A. Adesina  @akin_adesina  “My Darling Wife Grace (Yemisi) turns 60! Happy 60th birthday today my sweetheart, darling wife, and best friend. Your life is a blessing to me and many around the world. You are beautiful and adorable. I love you 60 times over. You are a treasure! Your sweetheart, Akin”.